               <head>TO THE HIGH AND <lb/>
<normalised orig="MIGHTIE" auto="true">MIGHTY</normalised> PRINCE, JAMES, <lb/>
BY THE GRACE OF GOD, OF <lb/>
Great <normalised orig="Brittaine" auto="true">Britain</normalised>, France, and Ireland, King; Defender <lb/>
of the Faith; and in all causes, and <normalised orig="ouer" auto="true">over</normalised> all persons, <lb/>
as well <normalised orig="Ecclesiasticall" auto="true">Ecclesiastical</normalised> as <normalised orig="Ciuill" auto="true">Civil</normalised>, within his <normalised orig="Maiesties" auto="true">Majesties</normalised> <lb/>
<normalised orig="Realmes" auto="true">Realms</normalised> and Dominions, next and <normalised orig="immediatly" auto="true">immediately</normalised> <lb/>
<normalised orig="vnder" auto="true">under</normalised> God, and according to the <lb/>
Word of God, <normalised orig="Supreame" auto="true">Supreme</normalised><lb/>
<normalised orig="Gouernour" auto="true">Governor</normalised>.</head>
