                  <lb/>
your <normalised orig="Highnesse" auto="true">Highness</normalised>, because we <normalised orig="doe" auto="true">do</normalised> all know you to be <lb/>
much more expert, in all <normalised orig="customes" auto="true">customs</normalised> and matters of <lb/>
the Christians, then <normalised orig="euer" auto="true">ever</normalised> was Agrippa in the customs <lb/>
of the <normalised orig="Iewes" auto="true">Jews</normalised>. <lb/>
2 Whereas therefore by that <normalised orig="priuiledge" auto="true">privilege</normalised> that all <lb/>
