your <normalised orig="Maiestie" auto="true">Majesty</normalised>, but rather with the more <normalised orig="awfull" auto="true">awful</normalised> regard <lb/>
thereof. For being my <normalised orig="selfe" auto="true">self</normalised> much too base and <lb/>
<normalised orig="altogither" auto="true">altogether</normalised> <normalised orig="vnworthy" auto="true">unworthy</normalised> to <normalised orig="craue" auto="true">crave</normalised> so great things of <lb/>
