<normalised orig="beene" auto="true">been</normalised>, but as slow to <normalised orig="speake" auto="true">speak</normalised>, so rude also to write, <lb/>
especially not being now acquainted with the <lb/>
Court language of our time. In which respect I cannot <lb/>
but acknowledge my <normalised orig="selfe" auto="true">self</normalised> as <normalised orig="vnfit" auto="true">unfit</normalised>, as <normalised orig="vnworthy" auto="true">unworthy</normalised> <lb/>
to <normalised orig="deale" auto="true">deal</normalised> in so great matters, as afterwards I <lb/>
<normalised orig="haue" auto="true">have</normalised> dealt in with them, that are much better able <lb/>
to handle the same, then such a one as I am. Though <lb/>
also I had <normalised orig="beene" auto="true">been</normalised> better able to manage such a matter <lb/>
according to the <normalised orig="waight" auto="true">weight</normalised> of it, yet two being better <lb/>
then one, in other <normalised orig="affaires" auto="true">affairs</normalised>, and a three-fold <normalised orig="Corde" auto="false">Cord</normalised>, <lb/>
not being quickly broken, I was the bolder to <normalised orig="craue" auto="true">crave</normalised> <lb/>
their <normalised orig="ayd" auto="true">aid</normalised> to your <normalised orig="Maiestie" auto="true">Majesty</normalised> herein: and that so much <lb/>
the more in respect of their <normalised orig="qualitie" auto="true">quality</normalised>, as well as of <lb/>
their number to whom I <normalised orig="haue" auto="true">have</normalised> petitioned. For as <lb/>
your <normalised orig="Maiestie" auto="true">Majesty</normalised> is the Head of this your <normalised orig="Kingdome" auto="true">Kingdom</normalised>, so <lb/>
your Nobles of the <normalised orig="vpper" auto="true">upper</normalised> House of Parliament, are <lb/>
as it were the Shoulders and <normalised orig="Armes" auto="true">Arms</normalised>, and the <normalised orig="Gentrie" auto="true">Gentry</normalised> <lb/>
of the <normalised orig="nether" auto="true">neither</normalised> House (as it were likewise) the Thighs <lb/>
